cial send-off after the ceremony.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/my-son-was-so-happy-hours-after-saying-i-do-indian-origin-newlywed-pilot-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-us/articleshow/131434421.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/my-son-was-so-happy-hours-after-saying-i-do-indian-origin-newlywed-pilot-killed-in-helicopter-crash-in-us/articleshow/131434421.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-01T10:45:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131435210,imgsize-929385.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[10 darkest regions on Earth where you can get the clearest views of planets, stars and the Milky Way]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131433800.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-darkest-regions-on-earth-where-you-can-get-the-clearest-views-of-planets-stars-and-the-milky-way/articleshow/131433800.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/10-darkest-regions-on-earth-where-you-can-get-the-clearest-views-of-planets-stars-and-the-milky-way/articleshow/131433800.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-01T10:31:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131434218,imgsize-1564864.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[2,000-year-old Roman marble bust found on Alicante beach may depict the goddess Venus]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131434181.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indi